  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"MOBA Brawl\" is a strategic card battle game. During multiple rounds of arena battles, you can choose heroes and purchase skills in the store, update the skill combinations and positions of heroes, and finally defeat your opponents. The official version will include features such as ladder battles, campaign mode, Steam achievements, and an illustrated handbook. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357910/extras/8cfd06edab11c74484d847ec3d746a0b.avif?t=1742554753\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357910/extras_big/8cfd06edab11c74484d847ec3d746a0b.avif?t=1742554753 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357910/extras/1b1d1fd4a63be5186a1f830a76346542.avif?t=1742554753\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357910/extras_big/1b1d1fd4a63be5186a1f830a76346542.avif?t=1742554753 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357910/extras/1825e9bcefcdd0771467047476f730ca.avif?t=1742554753\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357910/extras_big/1825e9bcefcdd0771467047476f730ca.avif?t=1742554753 width=800 height=448 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357910/extras/ac27a9098a50abd31601a125d658d3b2.avif?t=1742554753\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357910/extras_big/ac27a9098a50abd31601a125d658d3b2.avif?t=1742554753 width=800 height=444 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"MOBA Brawl\" is a strategic card battle game. During multiple rounds of arena battles, you can choose heroes and purchase skills in the store, update the skill combinations and positions of heroes, and finally defeat your opponents. The official version will include features such as ladder battles, campaign mode, Steam achievements, and an illustrated handbook. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357910/extras/8cfd06edab11c74484d847ec3d746a0b.avif?t=1742554753\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357910/extras_big/8cfd06edab11c74484d847ec3d746a0b.avif?t=1742554753 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357910/extras/1b1d1fd4a63be5186a1f830a76346542.avif?t=1742554753\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357910/extras_big/1b1d1fd4a63be5186a1f830a76346542.avif?t=1742554753 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357910/extras/1825e9bcefcdd0771467047476f730ca.avif?t=1742554753\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357910/extras_big/1825e9bcefcdd0771467047476f730ca.avif?t=1742554753 width=800 height=448 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357910/extras/ac27a9098a50abd31601a125d658d3b2.avif?t=1742554753\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3357910/extras_big/ac27a9098a50abd31601a125d658d3b2.avif?t=1742554753 width=800 height=444 /></span></p>",
